TopicTitle: I think my game is broken

Articles.Content:

Basically Unity3D is causing a bad request for window size from the window manager (wm), and most wm's are failing to handle it.

You can try running in fullscreen mode, a smaller window may also work or installing another desktop that uses a wm that doesn't have this issue.

The only one I know of is Xfce, at least up to 1920x1080
